                                   Compmap
     This dynamic web page uses Javascript and cascading style sheets to
   display hourly RUC2 model graphics, surface weather, and AFOS graphics.
     The user can overlay the different graphics to produce a web-based
                "composite map". SPC Graphical Composite Maps
                               Upper Air Maps
   SPC Upper Air Maps Maps and derived fields based on twice daily (00 and
              12 UTC) radiosonde data over the continental U.S.
                            Fire Weather Graphics
    Forecast maps for various fire weather variables based on the Eta and
                   RUC models.  SPC Fire Weather Graphics
                            Mesoanalysis Graphics
    SPC Hourly Mesoscale Analyses Severe weather analyses updated hourly
     and usually centered on an SPC risk area. Note: Experimental Only!
